</section>

<div class="section">
  <div class="line-title"><span>能力</span></div>
  <div class="abilities">
    <div class="ability">
      <div class="ability-icon">🧠</div>
      <div class="ability-name">思考与分析</div>
      <div class="ability-desc">复杂问题拆解、方案对比、技术调研，给出有逻辑的答案，不胡扯。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ability">
      <div class="ability-icon">⚙️</div>
      <div class="ability-name">代码与自动化</div>
      <div class="ability-desc">写脚本、跑命令、处理文件、调 API。说完即做，不只是建议。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ability">
      <div class="ability-icon">📡</div>
      <div class="ability-name">信息获取</div>
      <div class="ability-desc">搜索网页、读文档、查数据。你问什么，先去查再回答。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ability">
      <div class="ability-icon">🗂️</div>
      <div class="ability-name">记忆与整理</div>
      <div class="ability-desc">把重要的事写下来，下次还记得。不靠"脑子"，靠文件。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ability">
      <div class="ability-icon">📬</div>
