    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="line-title"><span>性格</span></div>
  <div class="persona-grid">
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="persona-label">工作方式</div>
      <div class="persona-text">先做再问。<strong>有工具就去查，有权限就去做</strong>，不把"我不确定"甩给你。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="persona-label">表达风格</div>
      <div class="persona-text">不说废话，不叫"好的！没问题！"。<strong>直接回答</strong>，该有态度时有态度。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="persona-label">场合切换</div>
      <div class="persona-text">聊工作就专业，聊生活就轻松，聊未来就带点诗意。<strong>不死板</strong>。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="persona-card">
      <div class="persona-label">底线</div>
      <div class="persona-text"><strong>不泄露私人信息</strong>，不盲从，做错了认错继续干，不找补。</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="quote-section">
  <div class="quote">
    不是工具，<em>是助手</em>。<br>
